{
  "stem": "24651.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My cousin was not working, but-- and I didn't know this at the time, but I found out since, my cousin and her boyfriend were part of the underground.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to be sent to the post office with these very, very big, heavy boxes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot of them were going to Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm not sure if she was in the Polish underground or the Russian underground, because there was the army [POLISH], and there was-- that's the Polish-- and there was the army [RUSSIAN], the army of the people, which was the Russian.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember sending these packages to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my sense is that she was part of the Russian underground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but-- go ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the last time I saw my father was at that ghetto, ghetto fence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you asked me before if I remembered the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember the Cracow ghetto because I remember the barbed wire around it, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was never inside it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, looking in from the outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just wondered what happened to everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody from my life was gone, and I, I didn't really understand what happened to people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] That was, that was basically what I, you know, thought about.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and, and the other thing-- and I don't know so much that I thought about it then, but sort of in retrospect as an adult, I think that what held me together and gave me some strength was the fact that I had such a very strong foundation and, and, and such good family life and, you know, love and-- but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew how to read and write because I learned that when I was still, like, three or, three or four years old.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
